Xupu County People's Congress Standing Committee; and others 
expressed their views on the development of counties and 
districts, the migration from reservoir areas, transportation 
projects, [words indistinct], the integration of policies, and 
so on. Governor Chen Bangzhu answered these questions one after 
another. 

