<H3> <TI>   Reportage on Second Session of Eighth NPC </TI></H3>
<H4>   Session Opens </H4>
<F P=102> OW1003011094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0103 GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1003011094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 10 (XINHUA) -- The Second Session of 
the Eighth National People's Congress [NPC] opened in the Great 
Hall of the People here this morning. 
  Qiao Shi, chairman of the NPC Standing Committee, declared 
the opening of the meeting. Premier Li Peng has begun 
delivering a government work report. 
  Attending today's meeting are Chinese Communist Party and 
Government leaders Jiang Zemin, Li Ruihuan, Zhu Rongji, Liu 
Huaqing and Hu Jintao. 

</TEXT>

