Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 11 (XINHUA) -- U.S. Secretary of 
State Warren Christopher and his party arrived here this 
evening, starting his four-day official visit to China. 
  W. Christopher came as guest of Chinese Vice-Premier and 
Foreign Minister Qian Qichen. 
  Among those greeting W. Christopher and his party at the 
airport were Chinese Vice-Foreign Minister Tian Zengpei and U.S. 
